Package: bRunching
Title: Bunching Correction Estimators for Censored Treatments
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hugo", "SantAnna", email = "hsantanna@uab.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Debora", "Mazetto", email = "dmazetto@tntech.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Author: Hugo SantAnna [aut, cre], Debora Mazetto [aut]
Maintainer: Hugo SantAnna <hsantanna@uab.edu>
Description: Implements the Caetano, Caetano, and Nielsen (CCN) bunching correction
    estimator for regression models with a treatment variable censored at zero.
    When many observations bunch at zero, naive OLS is biased. This package
    estimates the censored expectation under uniform, Tobit, or symmetry
    assumptions and includes it as a correction term. Supports homogeneous and
    heterogeneous treatment effects, heterogeneous correction terms, and
    discontinuity plots at the bunching point.
